flowchart TD
    A[Capacity boundary reached] --> B{Eviction profile}
    B -- NoEvictionPreBridgeProfile --> C[Emit ExtremeProfileInsufficientReport]
    B -- DelegateToReadSideProfile --> D[Emit CapacityDelegatedToReadSideReport]
    B -- FifoContainerEviction --> E[Select FIFO candidate]
    B -- OldestTimeRangeEviction --> F[Select oldest TContainerTimeRange]
    B -- EmergencyEvictionProfile --> G[Select emergency candidate]

    E --> H[Validate candidate]
    F --> H
    G --> H

    H --> I{Safe to evict?}
    I -- No --> J[Emit TEvictionRejectedReport]
    I -- Yes --> K{Active refs?}
    K -- Yes --> L[Invalidate / wait / reject]
    K -- No --> M{Active ingress / dispatch / round?}
    M -- Yes --> J
    M -- No --> N[Claim eviction safe point]
    N --> O[Apply eviction]
    O --> P[Update registry/waiting lists]
    P --> Q[Emit TEvictionAppliedReport]
